\newlabel{fig:cycle_boundaries}{{3.5}{17}{Running cycle boundaries detected by the autocorrelation-based detector overlaid on the \texttt {contact\_diff} signal for an example video (DUNG27). Alternating shaded bands correspond to individual FS-to-FS cycles; red dashed lines mark the detected boundaries. The periodic structure of the signal makes the boundaries reliably locatable by the autocorrelation procedure}{figure.caption.14}{}}
